{"body": "@JonRowe I made a patch on my project. Like this:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n# -*- encoding : utf-8 -*-\r\n# patch/errors\r\nrequire 'active_model'\r\n\r\nmodule ActiveModel\r\n  class ErrorMessage < String\r\n    def initialize msg, type\r\n      super msg\r\n      @type = type\r\n    end\r\n    \r\n    def type\r\n      @type\r\n    end\r\n  end\r\n\r\n  class Errors\r\n    alias origin_generate_message generate_message\r\n    def generate_message(attribute, type = :invalid, options = {})\r\n      ErrorMessage.new origin_generate_message(attribute, type, options), type\r\n    end\r\n  end\r\nend\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/14480431", "created_at": "2013-03-06T03:19:42Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7876#issuecomment-14480431", "updated_at": "2013-03-06T03:19:42Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7876, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/fsword", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/fc2590129d5efa61a05f476c27b71698?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ff4bd67327fd01a153081ab6cf611a0e6.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/received_events", "gravatar_id": "fc2590129d5efa61a05f476c27b71698", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "fsword", "type": "User", "id": 18908, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fsword/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f804bd3543c15100b1ba"}, "id": 14480431, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rail